title: SIMLockPatchGen_v2.2  This application can generate SIM-Lock rem
description:
SIMLockPatchGen_v2.2

This application can generate SIM-Lock remover (unlock) vkp patches what you can use with SETool2 Lite, 
Far Manager with jdflasher or SEFP plugins and compatible tools. 
It is able to generate vkp patches from DB2000/DB2010/DB2012/DB2020 CID36/49/50/51/52/53 
MAIN firmwares (*.mbn, *.bin).
